articles.title: Tech world won't have long to fall in line when EU signs off on AI Act - The Register
articles.description: Did your org already start baking AI into systems? Watch out. Staggered timetable for compliance expected after draft leaked
articles.content:
Users and builders of AI systems face a race against time to comply with incoming European legislation if lawmakers continue on their current trajectory.
